WEBVTT

00:00.400 --> 00:03.089
Carefully stow your hand luggage in the overhead bins...

00:03.207 --> 00:04.963
...or under the seat in front of you.

00:08.154 --> 00:11.199
When the seatbelt sign is on, please fasten your seatbelt.

00:11.439 --> 00:13.865
Keep it fastened and visible while seated.

00:15.453 --> 00:17.848
The crew will provide loop belts for infants.

00:19.481 --> 00:21.929
You can release it as shown here when needed.

00:22.829 --> 00:26.835
It is illegal to smoke on this flight, including electronic cigarettes.

00:27.116 --> 00:29.787
It is also strictly prohibited to smoke in the toilets,...

00:30.015 --> 00:31.812
...which are equipped with smoke detectors.

00:32.943 --> 00:36.783
Set your mobile phones and all electronic devices to flight mode.

00:37.471 --> 00:39.898
For takeoff and landing, please switch them off.

00:40.332 --> 00:42.388
Unplug them and stow them away.

